{"tid":2514551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LateShow 同 Bomba 真係高下立見","createTime":"2021-05-03T10:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T10:36:57.000Z","uid":30719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1451df4164757dc268314cfcf607a1d70c271318","tid":2514551,"uid":30719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"抽左幾點出黎比較，Bomba 真係垃圾徵費<br />\n<br />\n1. 以舊帶新<br />\n想發掘新人舊人退居二線冇問題，但正常都唔會一刀切。LateShow 搵左 d 舊有節目舊人 (杜文澤，走佬去台灣)  穩左個場先，再去提拔新人 (生秋王大師班出黎)，而 Bomba 就一刀切整個乜柒志游戀愛日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，入面 5 條友都唔知乜水，真係死忠先會支持，最後初始資金唔夠走向收皮之路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 節目數量<br />\nBomba 個 allShit 出片量幾少大家都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當初課比 LateShow 都已經有心理準備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但家陣 LateShow 真係比到好多驚喜我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次上去見到新片第一時間既反應係，嘩！又有新片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 籃黃<br />\nBomba 又想撐警又想打後生仔市場，fox 真係 on99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你撐警就拍警訊比廢老睇麻，定位錯尻哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啊，班死廢老應該冇乜消費力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己覺得 LateShow 立場近本土 <br />\n<br />\n4. 杜狗 vs Fox<br />\n兩個都差唔多囂架啦，但前者曾經係明星，後者係無料撐警撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cb2874627dc2343109cd469cbe7a16390dcb91","tid":2514551,"uid":30719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}